        "action": "Allow Number Plates To Be Spaced As Drivers Wish",
        "additional_details": "I strongly believe the government should allow number plates to be spaced as people wish. I believe this as witnesses may be able to easily recall a number plate if an offence was committed. I'm addition number plates may be easily reconasiable by law enforcement agencies which could help them reduce repeat offences.",
        "background": "I believe number plates should be able to be spaced as drivers wish. For example from \"AB99 ABC\" which is the current number plate spacing requirement to \"A B 99ABC\".",
